      <title>美联储戴利称最新数据显示货币政策正在发挥作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/fed-s-daly-says-latest-data-show-monetary-policy-is-working</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山联邦储备银行行长玛丽戴利表示，周五公布的通胀数据表明货币政策正在发挥作用，但现在判断何时降低借贷成本还为时过早。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/fed-s-daly-says-latest-data-show-monetary-policy-is-working</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 13:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
